  Locus:
    Page: 36
    Verse: 20
Tags:
  - Body
---
Don’t pay too much attention to the body. If you worry about the wellbeing
of your body, you identify with it more and more. Look upon it as a useful
vehicle： maintain it, fuel it properly and repair it if it breaks down,
but don’t become attached to it.
